Cook one package of Johnsonville Italian Sausage according to package directions. Bias-slice and keep warm. Julienne strip peppers and onion and set aside. In a large pan add olive oil and garlic and saute for about 30 seconds. Add vegetables to oil and garlic and saute an additional 5 minutes or until crisp tender. Add tomatoes and sliced Italian Sausage and heat through, seasoning to taste with salt and pepper.